            <h3>Effective Date: May 27th, 2015.</h3>
            <p>Ychef values your privacy in your personal information that you provide in connection with the Service. This Privacy Policy explains what information Ychef collects from you, why certain information is collected, and how we use the information you provide.</p>

            <h3>What Is The Scope Of Ychef ’s Privacy Policy?</h3>

            <p>This Privacy Policy is incorporated into the Terms of Service and the Chef Guarantee, and it applies to the information obtained by us through your use of the Site, the Service, and other Ychef  products and services. Capitalized terms used in this Privacy Policy and not otherwise defined shall have the meanings provided for those terms in the Terms of Service.</p>

            <h3>Will Ychef ’s Privacy Policy Change?</h3>

            <p>We may need to revise this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in the Service and the Site and to comply with applicable laws. We may change this Privacy Policy at any time and without prior notice, at our sole discretion. Updates to this Privacy Policy, including the effective date of the new Privacy Policy, will be posted on the Site. It is important that you review any changes to this Privacy Policy. Your continued use of the Site and the Service following our posting of any changes to this Privacy Policy means you agree with and consent to be bound by the new Privacy Policy. If you disagree with any changes to this Privacy Policy and do not want your information to be subject to the revised Privacy Policy, you will need to close your account. To close your Ychef  account, please email us at info@Ychefapp.com.</p>

